Download full version of map

de_hotelgellert_fly is a port of the de_hotelgellert map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

ORIGINAL RELEASE 2014

Double Bomb Scenario Mission.

Budapest, September of 2018. Square of St. Gellert is under high alert following new information gathered by intelligence services. 

While access of district I. is being blocked, disguised as hotel personnel an underground movement is planning to bomb the newly reconstructed building. 

Tactical team has been deployed to prevent the radicals causing damage to the art relic premises.

* Since the automatically generated navigation file will not work correctly on this map, I recommend purchasing a manual navigation file.

You can also make your own navigation file yourself.
